view.name: NYC Transit Subway Entrance And Exit Data
view.attribution: MTA Headquarters, New York City Transit
view.description: This data file provides a variety of information on subway station entrances and exits which includes but is not limited to: Division, Line, Station Name, Longitude and Latitude coordinates of entrances/exits.

Disclaimers.Limitations: These entrances are represented as accurately as possible but mistakes or errors may be found.  Some of the fields may change post release of this information; efforts will be made to update when necessary. Some other fields may contain information that changes due to a situation not present or obvious  at time of data release (such as an elevator or escalator being out of service; an entrance closed for temporary or permanent reason, staffing is reduced at a station, etc.).

Notes.Notes: Notes on data release May 2013 Service (route) information is updated. Entrances are updated for various stations. Vending availability and hours of part-time booth (agent) are introduced.
